2. Merge Overlapping Time Intervals
Problem Given a list of intervals [start, end], merge all overlapping intervals.
Example
[[1,3],[2,6],[8,10],[9,12]]
→ [[1,6],[8,12]]
What Netflix is testing
* Sorting + iteration
* Clean data transformation
* Thoughtful edge handling
Strong signals
* “I’ll sort by start time first”
* “I maintain a current window”
* Tests: already merged, single interval, touching edges
